  \ a wish to universe please find me an amazing company tomorrow. Next day some more\
  \ adventure water sports . Evening decided to go massage parlour. Being hesitant\
  \ to go to one . Went to a super chic massage parlour . Found a really hot chic\
  \ . Her name was TA. She must be around 23. Selected her for the same. We went to\
  \ the room. She held my hand and i was feeling a lot shy. First timer story for\
  \ me. We went to the room. She started undressing her. I don't know what was happening\
  \ and by the time i could come into senses. She laid her hands around my waist indressing\
  \ me. I was like this is something not right. I am straight but falling in love\
